sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { Container, Button } from "../../globalStyles"; import { InfoSec, InfoRow, InfoColumn, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, ImgWrapper, Img, SectionTitle } from "./Mooc.elements"; import { data } from "./data" function InfoSection({ primary, lightBg, topLine, lightTopLine, lightText, lightTextDesc, headline, description, buttonLabel, img, alt, imgStart, start }) { return ( <> Book and book chaper Published {data?.map((data, key) => { return ( <> On coursera Offered by Google, December 2020 heading subtitle ) })} ); } export default InfoSection;
